Package com.orders.cabinet.mapper

Interface ShopInfoCachRepositoryMapper

public interface ShopInfoCachRepositoryMapper
Mapper interface for converting between ShopInfoCache and ShopInfoCacheDTO.

This interface uses MapStruct to map fields between the ShopInfoCache entity and the ShopInfoCacheDTO data transfer object. This allows for seamless conversion between database entities and DTOs used in application layers.
